30.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/big-mac-cost-1536x1059.png 1536w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/big-mac-cost.png 1958w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73205" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/29/cost-of-a-big-mac-at-every-mcdonalds-in-the-united-states/big-mac-cost/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/big-mac-cost.png" data-orig-size="1958,1350" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="big mac cost" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/big-mac-cost-750x517.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/big-mac-cost-1090x752.png" /></a></p><p> Pantry &amp; Larder 制作的地图显示了截至 2023 年初美国<a href="https://pantryandlarder.com/mccheapest">每家麦当劳麦当劳巨无霸的成本</a>。正如您所料，东海岸和西海岸的价格更高。最贵的巨无霸位于马萨诸塞州李市，售价为 8.09 美元。我认为运往夏威夷和阿拉斯加会导致这些州的价格上涨。</p><p>但蒙大拿州和亚利桑那州发生了什么？根据<a href="https://www.bea.gov/news/2023/real-personal-consumption-expenditures-state-and-real-personal-income-state-and">区域价格平价</a>，蒙大拿州的成本往往低于全国平均水平，而亚利桑那州则处于中间位置。话又说回来，当你<a href="https://flowingdata.com/2021/03/25/income-in-each-state-adjusted-for-cost-of-living/">调整生活成本</a>时，这两个州的收入紧挨着垫底，所以我想这是有道理的。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/big-mac/" rel="tag">巨无霸</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/cost/" rel="tag">成本</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/mcdonalds/" rel="tag">麦当劳</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 7320