ot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ebird populations" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ebird-populations-750x624.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ebird-populations-1090x907.png" /></a></p><p>哈里·史蒂文斯利用众包数据库<a href="https://ebird.org/home">eBird</a>中的数据，为《华盛顿邮报》 <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/climate-environment/interactive/2024/bird-population-decline-united-states-maps/?pwapi_token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..HvpPUtofQ0ttFCD2LcRuRwPwza4_PqhTeOESw3mqQ_o&#038;itid=gfta">绘制了鸟类数量的变化图</a>。过去十年里，建筑的增加和气候变化导致许多物种的数量下降，但蓝鸟等一些物种却出现了增长。</p><p>请务必查看最后的互动内容，它可以让您搜索完整的物种列表。</p><p>勤奋的观鸟者在 eBird 上记录数据，他们可以用它来跟踪自己的观察结果。总的来说，研究人员可以利用这些数据生成可靠的模型。这个项目的规模仍然令人惊叹。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/birds/" rel="tag">鸟类</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ebird/" rel="tag">eBird</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/population/" rel="tag">人口</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/washington-post/" rel="tag">华盛顿邮报</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73195</post-id></item><item><title> ✚ 可视化工具和学习资源，2024 年 1 月综述</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/25/process-273-roundup/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 25 Jan 2024 19:30:46 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[The Process]]></category><category><![CDATA[roundup]]></category><guid ispermalink="false">https://flowingdata.com/?p=73177 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/25/process-273-roundup/"><img width="750" height="420" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-750x420.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-p