x420.png 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-1090x610.png 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-210x118.png 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-768x430.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73182" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/25/process-273-roundup/process-273-featured/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured.png" data-orig-size="1340,750" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="process-273-featured" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-750x420.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/process-273-featured-1090x610.png" /></a></p><p>欢迎来到<a href="https://flowingdata.com/category/the-process/">The Process</a> ，这是面向 FlowingData 会员的时事通讯，它更深入地介绍了图表的制作方式。我是弥敦道。每个月我都会收集有用的工具和资源来帮助制作更好的图表。这是今年的第一篇综述。但首先，有一点新闻。</p><p><a href="https://flowingdata.com/membership/">成为会员</a>即可访问此内容 - 以及教程、课程和指南。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73177</post-id></item><item><title>所有数独谜题的数学特征</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/25/mathematical-feature-in-all-sudoku-puzzles/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:58:39 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Infographics]]></category><category><![CDATA[math]]></category><category><![CDATA[Numberphile]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sudoku]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73189 </guid><description><![CDATA[For Numberphile, Simon Anthony explains the Phistomephel Ring. The shape always contains the&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/math/" rel="tag">数学</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/numberphile/" rel="tag">Numberphile</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/sudoku/" rel="tag">数独</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="arve" data-mode="normal" data-provider="youtube" id="arve-youtube-pezlnn4x52g65ba3788b44ca540281324" style="max-width:1090px;"> <span class="arve-inner"><span class="arve-embed arve-embed--has-aspect-ratio"><span class="arve-ar" style="padding-top:56.250000%"></span><iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen class="arve-iframe fitvidsignore" data-arve="arve-youtube-pezlnn4x52g65ba3788b44ca540281324" data-src-no-ap="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pezlnN4X52g?iv_load_policy=3&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;autoplay=0" frameborder="0" height="613.125" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-presentation allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox" scrolling="no" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pezlnN4X52g?iv_load_policy=3&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;playsinline=0&#038;autoplay=0" width="1090"></iframe></span></span> <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http:\/\/schema.org\/","@id":"https:\/\/flowingdata.com\/2024\/01\/25\/mathematical-feature-in-all-sudoku-puzzles\/#arve-youtube-pezlnn4x52g65ba3788b44ca540281324","type":"VideoObject","embedURL":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/pezlnN4X52g?iv_load_policy=3&modestbranding=1&rel=0&autohide=1&playsinline=0&autoplay=0"}</script></div><p>西蒙·安东尼 (Simon Anthony) 在 Numberphile 上解释了 Phistomephel 戒指。形状始终包含与角相同的数字。数学魔法！</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/math/" rel="tag">数学</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/numberphile/" rel="tag">Numberphile</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/sudoku/" rel="tag">数独</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73189</post-id></item><item><title> AI数据工具目录</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/24/catalog-of-ai-data-tools/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:20:07 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[AI]]></category><category><![CDATA[journalism]]></category><category><![CDATA[tools]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73165 </guid><description><![CDATA[Meant to be comprehensive more than a curated collection, the Journalist&#8217;s Toolbox AI&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/journalism/" rel="tag">新闻</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/tools/" rel="tag">工具</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Journalist&#39;s Toolbox AI 旨在提供全面的内容，而不仅仅是精心策划的集合，它提供了许多<a href="https://journaliststoolbox.ai/ai-driven-data-tools/">可以帮助您更有效地获取数据的工具</a>链接。或者至少使用更多类似人工智能的东西。</p><p>人工智能要足够可靠地分析和理解数据，还有很长的路要走。其中很多东西仍然感觉像是半生不熟的噱头。但是，对于可以轻松定义的机械重复任务（例如抓取或编码杂务），其中一些资源可能有用。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/journalism/" rel="tag">新闻</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/tools/" rel="tag">工具</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73165</post-id></item><item><title>还有哪里可以找到 FlowingData</title><link/> https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/23/where-else-to-find-flowingdata/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:24:54 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Site News]]></category><category><![CDATA[social media]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73168 </guid><description><![CDATA[You can always count on the site for updates on visualization, data, and&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/social-media/" rel="tag">社交媒体</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>您始终可以依靠该<a href="https://flowingdata.com/">网站</a>获取可视化、数据和统计数据的更新。还有<a href="https://flowingdata.com/feed">RSS</a>和<a href="https://flowingdata.com/newsletter/">电子邮件</a>。但有人告诉我你应该在他们所在的地方见见他们，所以这里是你可以找到 FD 的其他地方。</p><p> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/flowingdata/">Instagram</a> — 视觉。更常见的是发帖频率较低。我有一种感觉，这可能就是我社交媒体之旅的终点站。</p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/flowingdata">X/Twitter</a> — 曾经有一段时间，当我写书和论文时，我一直打开 Twitter 应用程序。这是一个有趣的想法和分享的地方。现在的情况很奇怪，而且似乎没有好转的迹象。所以我现在还在。</p><p> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/flowingdata/">LinkedIn——</a>哇哦。我不知道自己在这个以职业为中心的地方做什么。但每隔几周就会有人将我的一个项目作为自己的项目发布，并获得数千次互动，所以我就在这里。</p><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@flowingdatamoves/videos">YouTube——</a>有时我会用视频格式制作数据动画，效果更好。</p><p> <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/flowingd">Reddit——</a>以可视化为中心的 Reddit 子版块可能过于挑剔，而且纸上谈兵的图表专家的比例似乎很高。但我也想知道谁使用了 FlowingData 用户名并且多年前从未发布过。 （可能是我。）</p><p> <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/flowingdata.com">Bluesky——</a>就 Twitter 的替代品而言，这可能就是它了。但我不确定我是否想要替代方案。</p><p><a href="https://www.threads.net/@flowingdata">线程</a>——或者也许是这个？我不知道这太多了。</p><p><a href="https://vis.social/@flowingdata">乳齿象</a>——我在这里。看来这不适合我。我花了三次尝试才正确拼写<em>乳齿象</em>。</p><p> <a href="https://facebook.com/flowingdata">Facebook——</a>有点。 FD 页面已经存在很多年了，但我经常忘记它的存在。</p><p>社交媒体正处于十字路口，所以此时我正在尝试一切。到时候那里见。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/social-media/" rel="tag">社交媒体</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73168</post-id></item><item><title> DNA面对面识别试图找到嫌疑人</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/23/dna-face-to-facial-recognition-in-attempt-to-find-suspect/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:04:54 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistics]]></category><category><![CDATA[crime]]></category><category><![CDATA[DNA]]></category><category><![CDATA[ethics]]></category><category><![CDATA[facial recognition]]></category><category><![CDATA[privacy]]></category><category><![CDATA[Wired]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=73162 </guid><description><![CDATA[In an effort to find a suspect in a 1990 murder, there was&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/crime/" rel="tag">犯罪</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/dna/" rel="tag">DNA</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ethics/" rel="tag">道德</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/facial-recognition/" rel="tag">面部识别</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/privacy/" rel="tag">隐私</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/wired/" rel="tag">连线</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>为了寻找 1990 年谋杀案的嫌疑人，警方于 2017 年请求使用基于 DNA 的面部 3D 渲染。 <a href="https://www.wired.com/story/parabon-nanolabs-dna-face-models-police-facial-recognition/">Dhruv Mehrotra 为《连线》杂志报道</a>：</p><blockquote><p>该侦探要求通过面部识别技术对嫌疑人的面部进行 DNA 生成估计，此前尚未有报道。它是在透明度组织“分布式拒绝秘密”发布的大量被黑客入侵的警察记录中发现的，这似乎是警察部门尝试对根据犯罪现场 DNA 算法生成的面部进行面部识别的第一个已知实例。</p></blockquote><p>这似乎是一个自然的过程，但应该很容易看出，当某人的面部构造不佳，然后通过面部识别进行错误分类时，技术的配对可能会导致各种问题。人脸的置信区间相当于多少？</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/crime/" rel="tag">犯罪</a>, <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/dna/" rel="tag">DNA</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ethics/" rel="tag">道德</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/facial-recognition/" rel="tag">面部识别</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/privacy/" rel="tag">隐私</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/wired/" rel="tag">连线</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73162</post-id></item><item><title>所有河流流过的海洋</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/22/oceans-that-all-the-rivers-d