 data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-750x501.jpg" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-1090x728.jpg" /></a></p>河流流入海洋。草蜢地理通过颜色对世界上的河流进行编码...<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/drainage/" rel="tag">排水系统</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/grasshopper-geography/" rel="tag">蚱蜢地理</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ocean/" rel="tag">海洋</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/rivers/" rel="tag">河流</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/22/oceans-that-all-the-rivers-drain/"><img width="750" height="501" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-750x501.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-750x501.jpg 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-1090x728.jpg 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-210x140.jpg 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-768x513.jpg 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa.jpg 1552w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="73158" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/01/22/oceans-that-all-the-rivers-drain/ocean-drainage-usa/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa.jpg" data-orig-size="1552,1037" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="ocean-drainage-usa" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-750x501.jpg" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ocean-drainage-usa-1090x728.jpg" /></a></p><p>河流流入海洋。 《草蜢地理》根据流入的海洋对世界上的河流进行了颜色编码，并<a href="https://www.grasshoppergeography.com/collections/ocean-drainage-basin-maps">制作了一系列地图</a>。</p><blockquote><p>但是，我听到你们大多数人问，什么是海洋流域图？几年前，我试图找到一张地图，显示世界上每条河流最终都流向哪个海洋。我有点惊讶地发现没有这样的地图，所以我决定像往常一样自己制作它。好吧，在意识到所有的技术困难之后，我不再对它不存在感到惊讶了。</p></blockquote><p>它让我想起了显示<a href="https://flowingdata.com/2021/05/25/map-shows-you-where-a-raindrop-ends-up/">雨滴最终去向的</a>地图。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/drainage/" rel="tag">排水系统</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/grasshopper-geography/" rel="tag">蚱蜢地理</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ocean/" rel="tag">海洋</a>,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/rivers/" rel="tag">河流</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 73156 </post-id></item></channel></rss><!-- *´¨)
